thani oruvan ( english : the lone one ) is an indian 2015 tamil-language crime thriller film directed by mohan raja and written by subha . the film , produced by kalpathi s. &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , kalpathi s. ganesh and kalpathi s. suresh under the production company ags entertainment , stars jayam ravi and nayanthara . the plot revolves around ips officer mithran who wants to arrest siddharth abhimanyu , an affluent scientist who uses secret illegal medical practices for profit . the film 's soundtrack was composed by hiphop &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the cinematography and editing was handled by ramji and gopi krishna respectively . the film was released on 28 august 2015 . the film was remade in telugu as dhruva ( 2016 ) and in bengali as one ( 2017 ) . in 2017 , it was dubbed into hindi as double attack 2 by goldmines telefilms pvt ltd .